    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Re-pent-ance do I not pos-sess,__ nor yet e--ven___ an--y___ tears. Hence, O Sav-iour,__ Thee do__ I fer--vent---ly__ be---seech: Be-----fore___ the end___ con-vert____ me and grant re-pent-ance un--to__ me, that I may be saved__ from__ e-ter---nal pun--ish--ment.__"
